El_Monte.Valinda, California:
Valinda is a census-designated place (CDP) in the San Gabriel Valley, in Los Angeles County, California, in the United States. As of the 2010 census, the population was 22,822, up from 21,776 at the 2000 census.


== Geography ==
Valinda is located at 34°2′16″N 117°55′44″W (34.037760, -117.928939).
